OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fsunny and hot into this evening with
OL,7,Ftemperatures only slowly falling away
OL,8,Fafter dark. Clear skies continuing
OL,9,Fovernight and staying rather warm,
OL,10,Fmaking it quite uncomfortable for
OL,11,Fsleeping.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTemperatures rapidly rising
OL,14,Fin the strong sunshine and becoming
OL,15,Fhot inland by the afternoon. Very
OL,16,Flocalised thunderstorms may develop
OL,17,Flater. Some relief on many coasts with
OL,18,Fsea breezes possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
