OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fslightly fresher feel on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fbut still very warm with an easterly
OL,8,Fbreeze. Temperatures remaining above
OL,9,Faverage to end the week. Often sunny
OL,10,Fwith isolated showers or thunderstorms
OL,11,Fpossible.
